Averages are obviously imprecise but they paint a pretty clear picture here=
: you can abstract away a lot of complexity by thinking about startup valua=
tions as the probability that they can grow as large as Facebook, Amazon, A=
pple, Microsoft, or Google. The higher the valuations of the biggest tech c=
