oft or Apple (Google has been a slow-grower, not even quadrupling).&nbsp;</=
p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0=
 0 1em 0;">Looking at average US startup valuations versus both Apple and A=
